  "title": "Business Development Executive (IT Infrastructure/Cyber Security)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a <strong>Computer and Network Security Industry.</strong> Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a<strong> Business Development Executive</strong> to be part of their Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the <strong>West </strong>- easily accessible.<br /></p><p><strong>About the Role:</strong></p><p>Are you passionate about technology and eager to drive business growth in a fast-evolving field? We are looking for a proactive and ambitious <strong>Business Development professional</strong> to play a key role in expanding our cyber-security portfolio across Singapore and the APAC region.<br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Spot, evaluate, and pursue new business opportunities in priority industries and markets across the region.</li><li>Develop and implement go-to-market strategies to accelerate the adoption of our cyber-security solutions.</li><li>Build strong, consultative relationships with customers and partners, collaborating with internal technical teams when needed.</li></ul></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min Degree Cybersecurity, Computer Science, or a related field.</li><li>Minimum 1 year of experience in business development or sales </li></ul><p></p><p><em>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click </em><em><strong>APPLY NOW</strong></em><em> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</em></p><p><em>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</em><br /></p><p><em>Email Address: </em><a href=\"mailto:jobs@recruitpedia.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</em></a></p><p><em>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</em></p><p><em>EA License No: 19C9682</em></p><p><em>EA Personnel No: R25157233 (Loh Pooi Keng)</em></p>",
